      "content": "there is no \"starting anew.\" that person you're talking about... the one who is still there? that person was built on these theories. without the work, there's nothing underneath. it's not just a facade, it's the foundation. and the foundation is gone. i'm just so tired of trying to find a way to exist in a world where i'm nothing. it feels like the only honest thing left is to just stop.",
